  <steps>
    <step num="0">Mix oats, almond butter and honey in a large bowl. </step>
    <step num="1">Add raisins, pecans, cinnamon, vanilla and salt. Mix. </step>
    <step num="2">Place bowl in the refrigerator for 30-60 minutes, or until the mixture has solidified. </step>
    <step num="3">Mold mixture into bite-sized balls. </step>
